t/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。三個月後格林確認為電影的導演<ref name="BeginFilming">{{cite news|last1=Perry|first1=Spencer|title=Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 2 to Begin Filming Next Month|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/421787-teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-to-begin-filming-next-month#/slide/1|accessdate=2015-03-23|quote=Set to be directed by Earth to Echo‘s David Green, Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 2 is set for release on June 3, 2016.|publisher=comingsoon.net|date=2015-03-22|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924025352/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/421787-teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-to-begin-filming-next-month#/slide/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月，布拉德·福勒和安德魯·福姆表示，續集將於2015年4月在紐約和[[水牛城|水牛城]]開拍<ref name="BeginFilming" /><ref name="#1"/><ref>{{cite news|last1=FERMINO|first1=JENNIFER|title='Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 2' to film in New York City and Buffalo, bringing an estimated $70 million in spending|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-film-nyc-buffalo-article-1.2157366|accessdate=2015-03-21|publisher=nydailynews.com|date=2015-03-20|archive-date=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321080550/http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-film-nyc-buffalo-article-1.2157366|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[洛杉磯快艇|洛杉磯快艇]]的球員[[德安德魯·喬丹|德安德魯·喬丹]]、[[馬特·巴恩斯|馬特·巴恩斯]]、[[J·J·雷迪克|J·J·雷迪克]]、[[奧斯丁·瑞佛斯|奧斯丁·瑞佛斯]]和[[史賓瑟·霍斯|史賓瑟·霍斯]]也會客串演出<ref>{{cite news|last1=Wolfond|first1=Joe|title=5 Clippers to appear in Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 2|url=http://www.thescore.com/news/730718|accessdate=2015-03-26|publisher=thescore.com|date=2015-03-26}}</ref>。此外，CW的電視劇《[[綠箭俠_(電視劇)|綠箭俠]]》演員[[史蒂芬·艾梅爾|史蒂芬·艾梅爾]]將於續集中飾演凱西·瓊斯一角<ref>{{cite news|last1=Reyes|first1=Mike|title=Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 2 Is Adding A Few NBA Stars|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Teenage-Mutant-Ninja-Turtles-2-Adding-Few-NBA-Stars-70536.html|accessdate=2015-03-27|publisher=cinemablend.com|date=2015-03-26|archive-date=2020-11-